            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Cn</abbr><ex>aeo</ex></expan> Trebonio Fir<lb break="no" n="2"/>mo et <expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>eriae</ex></expan> Iantumarae <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Trebonius Faustus II<lb break="no" n="4"/>virum et <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ure</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>icundo</ex></expan> civitatis <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Aguont</abbr><ex>ensium</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>parentib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>optim</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> et sibi <lb n="6"/>et Treboniae Maximi <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iliae</ex></expan> Exoratae <lb n="7"/>coniugi <expan><abbr>fec</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>1944 durch Kriegseinwirkung zerstört. Z. 6: möglicherweise auch Maxim(i) fi(liae) statt Maximi f(iliae), da I mit F ligiert ist.</p>
            </div>
